### 2026-03-28 (Session 4)
- Deepened the audit of both Netease Cloud Music and Local Music Pro, then fixed playback-state desync issues caused by optimistic `setIsPlaying` updates and unhandled `audio.play()` promise rejections.
- Improved `LocalMusicApp.tsx` to properly clean up the `localmusic-dir-updated` event listener, clear stale library state when the directory changes, and prompt the user to rescan when the active directory does not match the cached DB.
- Refactored `backend/src/routes/localmusic.ts` DB persistence from a raw track array to `{ scannedDir, tracks }`, preserving backward compatibility while preventing cross-directory cache pollution.
- Upgraded local music streaming with MIME detection and invalid Range rejection to reduce playback glitches on non-MP3 files.
- Tightened `MusicApp.tsx` state handling for login refresh, playback failure fallback, and component unmount cleanup so the Netease player behaves more predictably under edge cases.

### 2026-03-28 (Session 5)
