- Hardened `frontend/src/apps/MusicApp.tsx` so songs without initial `cover` values proactively request `/api/system/music/detail`, updating both list rows and the current immersive player once the cover arrives.
- Reworked lyric parsing in both `MusicApp.tsx` and `LocalMusicApp.tsx` to support multi-timestamp LRC lines and lines without millisecond precision, improving synced lyric coverage.
- Added request-id guards for lyric loading in both players to prevent stale responses from an old song overwriting the current song's lyrics during rapid track switching.
- Improved Netease download marker refresh timing by performing multiple delayed refresh passes after pushing a task to Aria2, reducing the gap before “已下载” appears.

### 2026-03-28 (Session 6)
- Completed the deeper music hardening pass: both `MusicApp.tsx` and `LocalMusicApp.tsx` now use playback tokens plus pending seek restoration to avoid race conditions during rapid track switching, single-loop replay, and Netease quality changes.
- Replaced frontend-direct Netease Aria2 RPC submission with a dedicated backend `/api/system/music/download` route, which records `{ songId, filename, dir }` mappings in `~/.clawos/music_cache/netease_download_map.json`.
- Upgraded downloaded-track detection to prefer `songId` mapping over filename heuristics, significantly improving the reliability of local-priority playback and “已下载” badges after downloads complete.
- Improved Local Music Pro refresh behavior by reloading the library on window focus/visibility restore, helping the UI reflect freshly scanned or externally changed tracks without manual refreshes.

### 2026-03-28 (Session 7)
