- Fixed Netease cover backfill starvation in `MusicApp.tsx`: the previous global cover request id caused concurrent detail fetches to invalidate each other, so most missing album covers never appeared. Switched to per-song in-flight deduplication using `pendingCoverIdsRef`.
- Hardened song switch cleanup by resetting active song refs and pending cover state during teardown/directory change so late async responses cannot overwrite unrelated UI state.

